@Node "Wprowadzenie" "Track2File.guide/Introduction"

  Purpose of Track2File is ripping files written on NDOS disks.  Files
found can be saved on any device in original or decrunched form.

  Track2File is FREEWARE. Program and documentation must be spread in
unchanged form (archive). Any modifications are forbidden.

  This program uses following libraries:

  - reqtools - by Nico François and Magnus Holmgren

  - xfdmaster - by Georg Hormann

@EndNode

@Node "Wymagania sprzëtowe" "Track2File.guide/Requirements"
        
  Track2File requires any Amiga with OS 2.04 (V37) or higher.
  Recommended minimum memory size is 2MB.

@EndNode

@Node "Instalacja" "Track2File.guide/Installation"

  Copy Track2File, it's icon and documentation to any directory
  and contents of Libs directory to LIBS:

@EndNode

