  @{b}@{u}Version 1.15 (16.04.96) - recognizes 72 IDs@{uu}@{ub}

  Added new version of xfd.library, it allows to detect length of
  PowerPacked data file. Detection of 100KB file can take few minutes on
  not expanded Amiga 1200, but is 100% reliable.

  Program correctly detects length of files with TPWM headers.

  New headers:
