@Node "Od autora" "Track2File.guide/From author"

  Track2File is written in assembly language using Devpac v3.14. It
  was tested on Amiga 1200 + Blizzard IV 50 MHz + 8 MB Fast Ram + 2.5 GB
  Caviar HDD.

  If you have any ideas or you have found any bugs, write to me on address:

                       Mr.Larmer of Wanted Team
