@Node "Disk Read" "Track2File.guide/Disk Read"

  Disk Read

  Reads disk to memory.

@EndNode

@Node "Load File" "Track2File.guide/Load File"

  Load File

  Opens file requester. After selecting file name, loads it to memory.

@EndNode

@Node "Search" "Track2File.guide/Search"

  Search

  Scans allocated memory.  If file header is found requester with
  information about this file opens.  Then you can select:

 @{"Save file      " Link "Save file"}

 @{"Decrunch & save" Link "Decrunch & save"}

 @{"Abort          " Link "Abort"}

 @{"Continue       " Link "Continue"}

@EndNode

